Package: Spatialsmooth
Title: Spatial Transcriptomics Deconvolution Methods and Spatial smooth
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("njj", "yx", email = "njjyxl1006@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Spatialsmooth provides a toolset for spatial transcriptomics data analysis, focusing on spatial smoothing of deconvolution results. The package integrates the results of multiple deconvolution algorithms for spatial smoothing of cell type proportions through neural network modeling to improve the accuracy of cell type inference in spatial transcriptomics data. The package provides functions to run various spatial transcriptomics deconvolution methods, including CARD, RCTD, SPOTlight, SpatialDWLS, AdRoit, Seurat, Redeconve, and SpatialDecon.
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
